name: Delete a specific stories of a project

steps.name: Given I count all the stories of a project which exist in a account
Given I set up a "DELETE" request to "/projects/{proj_id}/stories/{stories_id}" endpoint
Then I get a "204" status code as response
And The length of the stories of a project is reduced by one

labels.name: feature
labels.value: Acceptance tests for stories of a project with read, update and delete
